# Cursor Rule: checkout

## Applies to
components/checkout/**/*

## Description
Rules for checkout flow, forms, and submission handling.

## Rules
- Use Formik or controlled inputs for consistency.
- Group address, payment, and review into logical steps.
- Validate input fields both client-side and server-side.
- Provide inline feedback for form errors.
- Use hooks to manage order submission.
